	<main>

		<section class="intro">
			<div class="text"><Text /></div>
			<img src="./anders1.jpg" class="photo" alt="" />
			<div class="subtitle">
				<p>I make people smile.</p>
				<p>
					Not by being funny, but by building things.
					For example applications, ideas and engineering teams. I currently work with cybersecurity at Bitwarden.
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="mailto:web@andersaberg.com">Email</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://github.com/abergs">Github</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/abergs/">LinkedIn</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://twitter.com/andersaberg">Twitter</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="work">
			<h2>Work</h2>
			<p>I'm the Director of Passwordless at Bitwarden.
				I've previously developed AI and products at Binary Brains. Earlier, I spent over a decade as a software enginner and CTO at Caspeco.</p>
		</section>
